nacional national explosives 
y subsequent to overt act x floyd carltoncacerez along 
with john jaironaranjo flew approximately 400 kilograms of cocaine 
from el cafital airstrip in colombia to coronado airstrip on the 
pacific coast of panama 
z in or about december 1983 floyd carltoncacerez met with 
manuel antonio noriega in panama concerning the price to be charged 
for the next cocaine shipment from colombia through panama 
aa subsequent to overt act z floyd carltoncacerez at the 
direction of manuel antonio noriega delivered 200000 in us 
