of visitors who have been giving the coyotes handouts she added 
they become habituated to people and conditioned to 
handouts she said they expect handouts and get bolder and 
bolder most of the time you can scare them away but some animals 
at old faithful can get quite bold 
she added that reports of beggar coyotes have been common in 
the park in past years and officials often heard reports of the 
animals approaching or running into people 
