california and other parts of the united states after a few days in 
a thai immigration facility 
nguyen van so has been trying to join his sister in oklahoma 
since he was freed in 1981 after six years years of confinement he 
said conditions in the camps were very very bad it was hard 
labor 
ho van phuoc a helicopter pilot who flew hundreds of missions 
