prodemocracy movements in eastern europe closely and hoped the 
revolution would come to their own country 
i hope the government will be good enough to understand the 
situation and open the society said nguyen cao son we dont 
want a situation like that in romania to happen in vietnam 
nicolae ceausescu the communist dictator of romania was 
overthrown and executed last month after a bloody uprising 
hundreds of thousands of vietnamese have been resettled in the 
united states since the war 
