fresh water fish commissions conservation program 
in exchange the state agreed to defer 13 misdemeanor charges 
filed against discovery island and five employees for abusing the 
vultures and other wild birds the state will drop all charges if 
the company and the employees adhere to all environmental and 
wildlife laws for the next year 
