the building he said a valve apparently was removed from the water 
main feeding the buildings fire sprinkler system thereby 
unleashing the flood 
a subway station across the street from the art decoera 
building also was flooded and was closed temporarily 
the fbi and gsa have jurisdiction over investigations regarding 
federal buildings 
